            <p>원본 대화와 프로필은 사용하지 않은 풍자 재구성입니다.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="chat-window">
            <div class="chat-title"><span>주주비상대책위원회 (4)</span><b>–––</b></div>
            <div class="message other"><i>Y</i><div><span>Y부장</span><p>하이닉스 250만 갈 때까지 허리띠 졸라맨다</p></div></div>
            <div class="message me"><div><p>지금 허리띠 몇 칸 남았어요?</p></div></div>
            <div class="message other"><i>Y</i><div><span>Y부장</span><p>300→240→220→200→168…</p><small>읽음 3</small></div></div>
            <div class="message system"><p>Y부장님이 방 이름을 ‘장기투자 연구회’로 변경했습니다.</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <div class="shell footer-inner">
        <div><strong>하이닉스 희망회로 발전소</strong><p>SK하이닉스와 무관한 비공식 풍자 사이트입니다.</p></div>
        <div class="disclaimer"><b>투자 유의</b><p>과거 주가는 미래 수익을 보장하지 않습니다. 모든 투자 판단과 희망회로 수리비는 본인 책임입니다.</p></div>
        <a href="#top">맨 위로 ↑</a>
      </div>
    </footer>

    <div class="toast" id="toast" role="status" aria-live="polite">링크 복사 완료. 단톡방에 투척하세요.</div>

    <script is:inline define:vars={{ priceData, hopeLines }}>
      const canvas = document.getElementById('priceChart');
      const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');
      const dpr = Math.min(window.devicePixelRatio || 1, 2);

      function drawChart() {
        const rect = canvas.getBoundingClientRect();
        canvas.width = rect.width * dpr;
        canvas.height = rect.height * dpr;
        ctx.scale(dpr, dpr);
        const w = rect.width;
        const h = rect.height;
        const pad = 12;
        const values = priceData.map((d) => d.value);
        const min = Math.min(...values) * 0.97;
        const max = Math.max(...values) * 1.03;
        const points = priceData.map((d, i) => ({
          x: pad + i * ((w - pad * 2) / (priceData.length - 1)),
          y: pad + (max - d.value) * ((h - pad * 2) / (max - min)),
        }));

        ctx.clearRect(0, 0, w, h);
        const gradient = ctx.createLinearGradient(0, 0, 0, h);
        gradient.addColorStop(0, 'rgba(255,47,69,.42)');
        gradient.addColorStop(1, 'rgba(255,47,69,0)');
        ctx.beginPath();
        ctx.moveTo(points[0].x, h);
        points.forEach((p) => ctx.lineTo(p.x, p.y));
        ctx.lineTo(points.at(-1).x, h);
        ctx.closePath();
        ctx.fillStyle = gradient;
        ctx.fill();

        ctx.beginPath();
        points.forEach((p, i) => i ? ctx.lineTo(p.x, p.y) : ctx.moveTo(p.x, p.y));
        ctx.strokeStyle = '#ff2f45';
        ctx.lineWidth = 4;
        ctx.lineJoin = 'round';
        ctx.stroke();

        const lowIndex = values.indexOf(Math.min(...values));
        const low = points[lowIndex];
        ctx.beginPath();
        ctx.arc(low.x, low.y, 7, 0, Math.PI * 2);
        ctx.fillStyle = '#101014';
        ctx.fill();
        ctx.strokeStyle = '#fff';
        ctx.lineWidth = 3;
        ctx.stroke();
      }
      drawChart();
      window.addEventListener('resize', drawChart);

      let count = 0;
      const quote = document.getElementById('hopeQuote');
      const countEl = document.getElementById('count');
      const powerText = document.getElementById('powerText');
      const powerBar = document.getElementById('powerBar');
      document.getElementById('generate').addEventListener('click', () => {
        count++;
        const line = hopeLines[(count - 1) % hopeLines.length];
        quote.classList.remove('pop');
        void quote.offsetWidth;
        quote.textContent = `“${line}”`;
        quote.classList.add('pop');
        countEl.textContent = `가동 ${count}회`;
        const power = Math.min(99, 92 + count);
        powerText.textContent = `${power}%`;
        powerBar.style.width = `${power}%`;
      });

      const toast = document.getElementById('toast');
      document.getElementById('share').addEventListener('click', async () => {
        try {
          if (navigator.share) await navigator.share({ title: document.title, text: '계좌는 냉각 중, 하이닉스는 반등 대기 중', url: location.href });
          else await navigator.clipboard.writeText(location.href);
          toast.classList.add('show');
          setTimeout(() => toast.classList.remove('show'), 2200);
        } catch (error) {
          if (error.name !== 'AbortError') location.hash = 'generator';
        }
      });
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
